if statement - Version 3: 
-------------------------
/*
Syntax:
if(condition 1)
{
  //if-body
}
else if(condition 2)
{
  //else if -body
}
else if(condition 3)
{
  //else if -body
}
else
{
  //else-body
}
--------------------------
